OL,3,CSecond Wimbledon expansion challenge
OL,4,Cgranted by judge
OL,6,FA campaign group has been given the
OL,7,Fgreen light to take a second legal
OL,8,Fbattle over the expansion of the
OL,9,FWimbledon tennis site to the Court of
OL,10,FAppeal.
OL,12,FSave Wimbledon Park (SWP) brought High
OL,13,FCourt legal action against the All
OL,14,FEngland Club over the expansion on the
OL,15,Fland of the former Wimbledon Park Golf
OL,16,FClub, claiming that it was subject to
OL,17,Fa statutory trust under a 150-year-old
OL,18,Flaw which restricted its use.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
