OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1784751301
OL,3,CSecond Wimbledon expansion challenge
OL,4,Cgranted by judge
OL,6,FLawyers for the club said the land was
OL,7,Fnever subject to a trust and, if it
OL,8,Fwas, it did not survive the club's
OL,9,F1993 purchase of the freehold.
OL,11,FMr Justice Thompsell found that the
OL,12,Fland "never became the subject of a
OL,13,Fstatutory trust", and that even if
OL,14,Fthis was wrong, the land was "never
OL,15,Fused or laid out for public
OL,16,Frecreation".
OL,26,@tD@FOUuD@PO]vD@^OUxD@KO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
