OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1784751301
OL,3,CSecond Wimbledon expansion challenge
OL,4,Cgranted by judge
OL,6,FThe plans could see the construction
OL,7,Fof 38 new tennis courts and an 8,000-
OL,8,Fseat stadium on the land, enabling the
OL,9,Fclub to host qualifying matches for
OL,10,Fthe tournament.
OL,12,FSeven maintenance buildings, access
OL,13,Fpoints and an area of parkland with
OL,14,Fpermissible public access are also
OL,15,Fplanned, along with work on Wimbledon
OL,16,FLake.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
