FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1784751301
OL,3,CSecond Wimbledon expansion challenge
OL,4,Cgranted by judge
OL,6,FThe Greater London Authority granted
OL,7,Fplanning permission for the expansion
OL,8,Fin 2024, a decision the High Court
OL,9,Fupheld last summer following a
OL,10,Fseparate legal challenge by SWP.
OL,12,FThe Court of Appeal has also given the
OL,13,Fgroup the go-ahead to challenge that
OL,14,Fdecision, which is yet to be heard.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/8
